Date: Sat, 26 Jul 2025 12:45:24 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] QSDK:CP: hostapd: ATF: Add init/deinit helpers

Add basic helper apis to support for Airtime Fairness (ATF),
which helps in managing the airtime distribution based on
ssid configs or ssid group configs or peer config.

Implement atf_offload_init()/atf_offload_deinit() api which
is per hapd_interfaces specific and has reference to atf_algo
of all per-radio interfaces (hostapd_iface).

Add atf_init_algo() and atf_deinit_algo() to allocate memory
when new hostapd_iface is created and deinit during interface
clean up.

Add atf_offload config which would be the master flag to enable
the atf feature.

Signed-off-by: Harshitha Prem <hprem@qti.qualcomm.com>
